OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start this
OL,6,Fmorning with some patchy rain or
OL,7,Fdrizzle, especially over higher
OL,8,Fground. Some brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping across the south during the
OL,10,Fafternoon, whereas northern areas
OL,11,Fseeing some further rain. Winds
OL,12,Ftending to strengthen later.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA band of heavy rain and
OL,15,Fstrong winds will move eastwards this
OL,16,Fevening. Rain clearing during the
OL,17,Fearly hours allowing some clearer
OL,18,Fspells and a few showers to follow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
