OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA brighter but breezy day
OL,6,Fon Wednesday with a mix of cloud and
OL,7,Fsunny spells. A few showers possible,
OL,8,Fespecially across the north of the
OL,9,Fregion. Temperatures near normal.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWet
OL,12,Fand windy on Thursday with gales
OL,13,Fpossible for a time. Colder on Friday
OL,14,Fwith blustery showers, occasionally
OL,15,Fwintry, especially in the north. Drier
OL,16,Fand less cold on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
